translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,102,"Yeh hai Allah tumhara Rubb, koi khuda uske siwa nahin hai, har cheez ka khaliq, lihaza tum usi ki bandagi karo aur woh har cheez ka kafeel hai"
  6,103,"Nigahein usko nahin paa sakti aur woh nigaahon ko paa leta hai, woh nihayat bareek been aur ba-khabar hai"
  6,104,"Dekho, tumhare paas tumhare Rubb ki taraf se baseerat ki roshniyan aa gayi hain, ab jo beenayi se kaam lega apna hi bhala karega aur jo andha banega khud nuqsan uthayega, main tumpar koi paasbaan(keeper) nahin hoon"
  6,105,"Is tarah hum apni aayat ko baar baar mukhtalif tareeqon se bayan karte hain aur is liye karte hain ke yeh log kahein tum kisi se padh aaye ho, aur jo log ilm rakhte hain unpar hum haqeeqat ko roshan kardein"
  6,106,"(Aey Muhammad)! Us wahee ki pairwi kiye jao jo tumpar tumhare Rubb ki taraf se nazil hui hai, kyunke us ek Rubb ke siwa koi aur khuda nahin hai. Aur in mushrikeen ke peechey na pado"
  6,107,"Agar Allah ki mashiyat hoti to (woh khud aisa bandobast kar sakta tha ke) yeh log shirk na karte, tumko humne inpar pasbaan (guardian) muqarrar nahin kiya hai aur na tum inpar hawaladaar ho"
  6,108,"Aur (Aey iman laney walon!) yeh log Allah ke siwa jinko pukarte hain unhein gaaliyan na do, kahin aisa na ho ke yeh shirk se aagey badhkar jahalat ki bina par Allah ko gaaliyan dene lagein. Humne to isi tarah har giroh ke liye uske amal ko khushnumna bana diya hai, phir unhein apne Rubb hi ki taraf palat kar aana hai, us waqt woh unhein bata dega ke woh kya karte rahey hain"
  6,109,"Yeh log kadi kadi kasamein kha kha kar kehte hain ke agar koi nishani hamare saamne aa jaye to hum uspar iman le aayenge. Aey Muhammad! Inse kaho, ke â€œnishaniyan to Allah ke paas hainâ€ aur tumhein kaise samajhaya jaye ke agar nishaniyan aa bhi jayein to yeh iman laney waley nahin"
  6,110,"Hum usi tarah inke dilon aur nigaahon ko pher rahey hain jis tarah yeh pehli martaba uspar iman nahin laye thay, hum inhein inki sarkashi hi mein bhatakne ke liye chodhe dete hain"